\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-360\li360\ulnone The Chamilo 2.0 platform now has a virtual course called Repository, to allow uploading items without publishing them. Making a Subject with only this virtual course in it allows keeping non-published objects synchronized.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}In Chamilo 2.0, published objects will now correctly be shared with other course administrators.\lang1033\ul\b\par
\lang1043\ulnone\b0{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}A new type of question (Type gaps dropdown) has been added. This type's syntax is the same as "Fill in the Gaps", but the multiple answers in gaps are shown as dropdown menu on the platform.\lang1033\ul\b\par
