{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Trying to generate statistics from Chamilo 2.0 no longet crashes the program.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}A bug that occurred when checking if an object existed on the Chamilo 2.0 platform has been fixed.\par
